 RTS         .BEND;---------------------------------------BPUTRAHEXCXY         .BLOCK         PHP         JSR A2HEX         LDA #<A2HEXPOS         LDY #>A2HEXPOS         JSR BPUTSCXY         PLA         PLP         RTS         .BEND;------------------------------------